{"books":[{"id":"whb","name":"文汇报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"从小，你就是提琴手献给优秀的共产党员张志新","authors":["徐刚"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":7,"day":4}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐刚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从小，你就是提琴手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"音乐，陶冶了你的性格，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也给多少人以美的享受"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总希望花儿开得红艳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总希望果儿结得甜透。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总希望十五的月亮下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甜蜜的江水不尽流……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"琴弦上可曾落百鸟?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱不够!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你歌唱生活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你热爱生活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你象小鸟一般向往着:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天白云，春光似酒……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的美丽，加上你的琴声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使你的内心比谁都富有!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从小，你就是提琴手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也曾给你丰富的报酬:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你有宁静的校园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你有情侣的追求，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昆明湖中清悠悠的水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等你去泛舟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风来唱，浪来和，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凌霄殿角伸出头……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从小，你就是提琴手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是个宁静的夜晚?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是黎明刚刚到来的时候?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写罢入党申请书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思悠悠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红岩上的江姐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顿时站立在心头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"‘红岩上，红梅开’……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌随白云远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮志几时酬?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从小，你就是提琴手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"‘四人帮’"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸出了罪恶的黑手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有几个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灭绝人性的刽子手!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要创造?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捆住手脚!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要唱歌?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卡住咽喉!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要思索?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"判作死囚!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你昂然地走向刑场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象去作最后的演奏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪响远不是生命的终结，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杜鹃喋血依然放歌喉!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从小，你就是提琴手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从小，你就是提琴手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你长跟在大地的怀抱里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身边是瀑布与河流:……，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是悠长而响亮的琴弦呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任你作芦笛声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任你作惊雷吼!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拨动它们的是看不见的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是真诚的心在真的演奏!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你唱呵，唱呵:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱道路曲折，前途光明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱浩浩江河，永远奔流……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假若道路不是通向共产主义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假若人间再能容得杀人凶手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么，到时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上与地下都不会沉默，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死去和活着的壮士将一起战斗!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"君不见?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火山的爆发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也只是因为压迫太久……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美好唱不尽，丑恶仍然有，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"归来呀，英魂!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从小，你就是提琴手。"}],"comments":[],"origin":"","comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}